{"tid":325040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒品害人] 16歲仔吞53包海洛英 疑太辛苦嘔吐被揭運毒","createTime":"2017-07-17T02:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T10:41:00.000Z","uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a8da35b6830d3e8ef351b6ff5c61343f5ba49fc","tid":325040,"uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"重慶黔江區公安局早前，成功破獲一宗跨省販運毒品案。16歲少年體內運毒，在機場因太辛苦嘔出而被拘捕，檢獲53包海洛英，淨重266.8克。<br />\n一個叫小龍（化名）的16歲青年，以體內藏毒方式運輸毒品，原定乘坐國內航線由雲南昆明機場起飛至重慶黔江。惟他在候機室因吞食毒品過多，覺得很難受在廁所吐出9包毒品。他其後用水洗淨後將毒品放入一個有檳榔圖案的塑料袋裝好，然後放在左褲袋內。<br />\n但過程被機場的工作人員發現，當小龍到達黔江時被由機場支隊警察及三名特警組成拘捕，並在其短褲左褲袋內搜獲9包毒品、一部手機及百元現金。在警員的監督下，小龍從體內排出44包毒品，每包約重6克。經鑑定及稱量，共繳獲53包海洛英，淨重達266.8克。<br />\n<br />\n小龍供稱，因父母離異，初中肄業的他便在其父親開的商店打工。一個偶然機會，無所事事的他被人拉進一個群，並被一名中介以「運一趟貨一萬元，並負責差旅費用」所誘惑而犯事。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://download.sina.com.hk/news/article/20170713/0/1/4/16%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%80%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E5%A0%B1%E9%85%AC-%E5%90%9E53%E5%8C%85%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%9B%E8%8B%B1%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%98%94%E5%90%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-7678711.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdownload.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20170713%2F0%2F1%2F4%2F16%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2585%25AC-%25E5%2590%259E53%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25B4%259B%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2598%2594%25E5%2590%2590%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-7678711.html&d=Sp%2FNz%2F8erNS03dKooJ%2FQ2cVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5d32f0a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://download.sina.com.hk/news/article/20170713/0/1/4/16%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%80%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E5%A0%B1%E9%85%AC-%E5%90%9E53%E5%8C%85%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%9B%E8%8B%B1%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%98%94%E5%90%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-7678711.html</a><br />\n<br />\n又一條on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過身為支那狗又有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後送多條毒品求助熱線: 186-186<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奉勸各位切勿以身試法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbd81c792b95ee92b843c4e8f6252b04bd4e8c3","tid":325040,"uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c69be901e08f4b342ca899ce87635b90dd880c","tid":325040,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一陣包野穿咗中毒死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd8dbe2f953288acb74baaf2ad6dcd64cf8099b","tid":325040,"uid":60527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一陣包野穿咗中毒死<img src=\"/asse